headline: CHEEZ-IT® OPENS STUDIO CHEEZ, THE ULTIMATE PARTY EXPERIENCE, SATISFYING LATE NIGHT CRAVINGS AND SPINNING CLUB HITS IN NYC
summary: We've all been there – it's midnight, the music's popping, the dance floor's packed and just as the night hits its peak...so does the craving for something delicious. What if those late night cravings didn't end the night, but instead turned it up? Introducing Studio Cheez: a one-of-a-kind Cheez-It® nightclub experience where late night cravings don't put an end to the party — they make it even more irresistible.
